lass="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;url&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;auto.c3pool.org:19999&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;user&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;YOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;pass&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;x&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;rig-id&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;nicehash&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;keepalive&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">true</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;enabled&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">true</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;tls&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;tls-fingerprint&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;daemon&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;socks5&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;self-select&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>            <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;submit-to-origin&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><br>        <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;print-time&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">60</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;health-print-time&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">60</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;dmi&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">true</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;retries&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;retry-pause&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;syslog&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;tls&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;enabled&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;protocols&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;cert&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;cert_key&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;ciphers&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;ciphersuites&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;dhparam&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><br>    <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;dns&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;ipv6&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>        <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;ttl&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">30</span><br>    <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;user-agent&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;verbose&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;watch&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">true</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;rebench-algo&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;bench-algo-time&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">20</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;pause-on-battery&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;pause-on-active&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">false</span></span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中第69行<code>YOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS</code>改称你的门罗币钱包地址</p><h2 id="创建XMR钱包"><a href="#创建XMR钱包" class="headerlink" title="创建XMR钱包"></a>创建XMR钱包</h2><p>打开网址<a href="https://wallet.mymonero.com/">MyMonero</a></p><p>  点击Create new wallet</p><p>  同意协议后，下一步，会出现门罗币钱包助记符，这个<code>一定要记住</code>，除非你只是注册玩玩，忘记了没有人会帮助你</p><p>  创建打开钱包后，看见钱包余额下面长乱码，就是钱包地址，点击COPY，替换YOUR_WALLET_ADDRESS</p><p>Ctrl+x输入y保存回车，执行命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./xmrig<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果使用c3矿池的软件测试结束后会出现configuration类似的语句，此时开始正式挖矿</p><p>官方挖矿软件会直接开始挖矿</p><blockquote><p>68行url选项是指定矿池地址，这里是c3-pool矿池，详情访问官网查看挖矿数据</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    
